{"id":48,"parent_id":47,"book_id":22674,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":48,"title":"June: Priesthood and Priesthood Keys","subtitle":"","short_title":"June: Priesthood and Priesthood Keys","uri":"/youth/learn/ap/priesthood-keys/overview","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"article","uri":"/youth/learn/ap/priesthood-keys/overview"},[".heading",["h1","June: Priesthood and Priesthood Keys"]],[".bodyBlock",[".topic",["p.para",["i","“The keys of the kingdom of God are committed unto man on the earth” (",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/65.2"},"D&C 65:2"],")."]],["p.para","The outlines in this unit will help each young man “learn his duty, and to act in the office in which he is appointed, in all diligence” (",["a",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.99"},"D&C 107:99"],"). In this unit, you can help the members of your quorum see how they can bless Heavenly Father’s children through their worthy exercise of the priesthood."],["p.para","To make Duty to God part of the Sunday quorum meeting, you may consider teaching the Duty to God outline below during this unit."],[".outlines",[".circles",["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/youth/bc/youth/content/images/priesthood-ap.jpg"}]],["h2","Outlines to choose from this month:"],["ul.bullet",["li",["p.para",["a",{"href":"/youth/learn/ap/priesthood-keys/worthiness"},"How does worthiness affect priesthood power? (Duty to God)"]]],["li",["p.para",["a",{"href":"/youth/learn/ap/priesthood-keys/what"},"What is the priesthood?"]]],["li",["p.para",["a",{"href":"/youth/learn/ap/priesthood-keys/keys"},"What are the keys of the priesthood?"]]],["li",["p.para",["a",{"href":"/youth/learn/ap/priesthood-keys/duties"},"What are my duties as an Aaronic Priesthood holder?"]]],["li",["p.para",["a",{"href":"/youth/learn/ap/priesthood-keys/mission"},"Why should I serve a mission?"]]]]],["h2","Mutual"],["p.para","Many of the lesson topics and learning activities in this unit would work well as Mutual activities. Work with quorum presidencies in selecting and planning appropriate activities to reinforce what the young men learn on Sunday."],["h2","Duty to God"],["p.para","The following sections from the",["i","Duty to God"],"book relate to the lessons in this unit:"],["p.para","“Live Worthily,” pages",["a",{"href":"/manual/fulfilling-my-duty-to-god-for-aaronic-priesthood-holders/deacon-spiritual-strength.f6"},"16–17"],",",["a",{"href":"/manual/fulfilling-my-duty-to-god-for-aaronic-priesthood-holders/teacher-spiritual-strength.f7"},"40–41"],",",["a",{"href":"/manual/fulfilling-my-duty-to-god-for-aaronic-priesthood-holders/priest-spiritual-strength.f7"},"64–65"]],["p.para","“Understand Doctrine,” pages",["a",{"href":"/manual/fulfilling-my-duty-to-god-for-aaronic-priesthood-holders/deacon-spiritual-strength.f11"},"18–20"],",",["a",{"href":"/manual/fulfilling-my-duty-to-god-for-aaronic-priesthood-holders/teacher-spiritual-strength.f12"},"42–44"],",",["a",{"href":"/manual/fulfilling-my-duty-to-god-for-aaronic-priesthood-holders/priest-spiritual-strength.f11"},"66–68"]],["p.para","“Priesthood Duties,” pages",["a",{"href":"/manual/fulfilling-my-duty-to-god-for-aaronic-priesthood-holders/deacon-priesthood-duties.head1"},"22–29"],",",["a",{"href":"/manual/fulfilling-my-duty-to-god-for-aaronic-priesthood-holders/teacher-priesthood-duties.head1"},"46–53"],",",["a",{"href":"/manual/fulfilling-my-duty-to-god-for-aaronic-priesthood-holders/priest-priesthood-duties.head1"},"70–77"]]]]]]],"refs":null}
